        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".) The result of seeing His glory was that he spake of Him. This is St. John’s interpretation of the prophecy. Isaiah himself tells us, “I saw also the Lord sitting upon a throne, high and lifted up, and his train filled the temple” (",
